{"tid":1716430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「毅進仔，執石仔。」嘅英文？","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:50:47.000Z","uid":76332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9842a7914be407222eb5c9eb464fb5b15e678a57","tid":1716430,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong Police. Clean up the streets! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n有唔少指揮官都係鬼佬 講中文又點照顧到佢地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有外國傳媒呢？要比全世界知道 香港警甴喺香港先係曱甴 地底泥 人人得而誅之<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次見到曱甴清rb 大家可以大嗌...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong Police. Clean up the streets! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d938bab467e39628d56642ef177a90a83aa0233","tid":1716430,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong Police. Clean up the streets! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>[/quote]"},{"pid":"420f6740de27939538187875091d333234b222b2","tid":1716430,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong Police. Clean up the streets! <img src=\"/assets/faces/n